  "instructions": [
    "Heat the clay pot over medium-high heat on the stovetop.",
    "Add the clarified butter and let it melt.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it's browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the cumin powder, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the dried cranberries, water, and red wine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and then reduce the heat to medium-low.",
    "Cover the clay pot with a lid and let it cook for 1 hour.",
    "Remove the lid and let it cook for another 30 minutes, or until the beef is tender.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs."
